| {{flagicon|CAN}} [[Spanish Canadian]] || 325,730 (1%) ||<ref name=cen2006>{{cite web |url=http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/english/census06/data/highlights/ethnic/pages/Page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo=PR&Code=01&Data=Count&Table=2&StartRec=1&Sort=3&Display=All&CSDFilter=5000 |title=Ethnocultural Portrait of Canada Highlight Tables (2006 Census) |accessdate=21 June 2009 |publisher=[[Statistics Canada]]}}</ref> || Self-description
