{{Infobox language |name=Winyé |nativename=Kolsi |states=[[Burkina Faso]] |speakers=20,000 |date=1999 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Niger-Congo |fam2=[[Atlantic–Congo]] |fam3=[[Gur languages|Gur]] |fam4=Southern |fam5=[[Gurunsi languages|Gurunsi]] |fam6=Western |iso3=kst |glotto=winy1241 |glottorefname=Winye }} '''Winyé''', or '''Kolsi''', is a [[Gur languages|Gur]] language of [[Burkina Faso]]. Speakers are largely monolingual.
